sudokuGame

Class Node<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • sudokuGame.Node<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - There are two types of T values we have, there are Primitive and there are Terminal,and both are extended from abstract TerminalOrPrimitive class.

    class Node<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Node is our basic binary tree, we use this class to build our Tree-based Genetic Programing. We prefer to build our tree to make the code more flexible, and easier to build and call all our recursive functions.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Abedalrhman Nsasra
    See Also:
    TerminalOrPrimitive, Primitive, Terminal
